These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, baking, gardening, traveling
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, thriller, western, horror
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, surfing, skateboarding, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, car, bus, trike
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##8
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 3. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8
 6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
 8. the person watching horror movies is between the person driving the car and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 9. the person driving the trike is the person watching western movies##1
10. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
13. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
14. the person who's hobby is baking is the person driving the bus##1
15. the person who's hobby is baking is not the person who's sport is surfing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | photography     | baking   | traveling | gardening |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | horror   | time-travel   | western  |
| Sport         | surfing  | skateboarding  | snowboarding  | climbing |
| Transport     | quad-bike    | bus | car     | trike    |

