.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, juice
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, potato, pomegranate, peach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, hip-hop, punk, gospel
4 different pets are kept: mouse, snake, hedgehog, guinea-pig
 1. the fan of punk is between the owner of the mouse and the fan of hip-hop##2
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
 4. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
 5. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the fan of hip-hop##8
 6. the person eating peach is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of reggae is the owner of the snake##1
10. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
11. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the fan of punk##8
12. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
13. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5
14. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
15. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
17. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the fan of hip-hop##8
18. the person eating potato is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
19. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | cola | hot-chocolate | juice  | iced-tea  |
| Food          | peach     | potato | cabbage | pomegranate  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop    | punk  | gospel | reggae |
| Pet           | hedgehog | guinea-pig | mouse    | snake  |

