 1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 3. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the fan of rock##5
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the right of the person watching sports movies##8
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the left of the person watching animation movies##8
 7. the fan of metal is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1
11. the person watching sports movies is not to the left of the fan of reggae##8
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
