.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-4::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, lemon, carrot, orange
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, skydiving, photography, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, firefighter, teacher, doctor
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, handball, snowboarding, climbing
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is not the chef##6
 2. the doctor is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 3. the person eating orange is the teacher##1
 4. the person eating lemon is between the chef and the firefighter##2
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person eating lemon##8
 7. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the doctor##1
10. the firefighter is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is not to the right of the person eating cherry##8
12. the chef is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
13. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
14. the firefighter is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
