 3. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
 5. the person driving the roller is the colombian##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the british##8
 7. the person drinking coffee is not the german##6
 8. the police-officer is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the person drinking coffee##7
 9. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
11. the chef is on the right of the photographer##1
12. the police-officer is not the pakistani##6
13. the british is somewhere to the right of the person drinking coffee##5
14. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
15. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the police-officer##8

