.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, sprite, almond-milk, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, r&b, punk, classical
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, volleyball, biathlon, golf
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, roller, ship, airplane
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is golf##1
 2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
 6. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 8. the person driving the roller is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
 9. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the person drinking sprite is not to the right of the fan of r&b##8
11. the fan of punk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
12. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | tea     | almond-milk    | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | classical      | punk     | r&b     |
| Sport         | basketball | biathlon  | golf     | volleyball  |
| Transport     | train     | ship | airplane | roller     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, fanta, 7up
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, filmmaking, hiking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, disco, funk, salsa
There are 4 different nationalities: french, japanese, thai, mexican
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the mexican##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
 3. the person drinking 7up is the fan of disco##1
 4. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 5. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the thai##3
 9. the japanese is not to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
10. the fan of funk is not the french##6
11. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
12. the mexican is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the fan of salsa is not to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
14. the french is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | 7up  | fanta | mirinda        |
| Hobby         | hiking | cooking   | collecting   | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | disco   | funk    | r&b      |
| Nationality   | japanese   | mexican | thai   | french    |

