.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, soy-milk, water, mirinda
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, teacher, software-developer, journalist
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, mouse, guinea-pig, dog
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, roller, trike, car
 1. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 2. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the teacher##8
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking coffee##1
 4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 6. the person driving the car is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the journalist is not to the right of the person driving the car##8
 8. the software-developer is on the far right##1
 9. the teacher is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
10. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
13. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the journalist##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | soy-milk          | coffee | water        | mirinda    |
| Job         | journalist | chef   | teacher | software-developer  |
| Pet         | guinea-pig           | rabbit     | dog       | mouse  |
| Transport   | car            | trike   | roller     | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, tea, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, skydiving, reading
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, musician, police-officer, lawyer
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, van, motorbike, car
 1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the person drinking tea##6
 2. the librarian is not to the left of the person driving the car##8
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is the person driving the van##1
 4. the librarian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##8
 5. the musician is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the left of the police-officer##8
 9. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
10. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere between the person driving the car and the lawyer##7
11. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | tea        | iced-tea        | almond-milk        | milk   |
| Hobby       | hiking      | cooking      | reading | skydiving |
| Job         | lawyer | police-officer | musician     | librarian  |
| Transport   | motorbike          | airplane      | van     | car  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, card-games, gardening, rock-climbing
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, project-manager, dancer, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, documentary, zombie, disaster
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, pop, gospel, funk
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the designer##8
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 3. the fan of funk is somewhere to the right of the fan of gospel##5
 4. the chef is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the dancer##6
 6. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the fan of pop##8
 7. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the dancer##8
 8. the dancer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
 9. the fan of gospel is in an even position##4
10. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
11. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the dancer and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
13. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing    | gardening   | reading   | card-games |
| Job           | designer | project-manager    | dancer | chef    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie   | family | documentary     | disaster    |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | gospel      | pop         | funk     |

 